    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but some of the guys are saying the tax credits don't really cover the actual cost of the gear and the extra paperwork, so it feels more like a penalty than an incentive. it's basically a choice between going green or staying in business. do you think these regulations are actually practical for small shops, or are they mostly designed with big corps in mind who can actually afford to pivot?",
